We checked this place out because of positive reviews on Yelp.
This looks like a real find.
We did take out and it was all very good.
The food came out very quickly too and it was handed to me by the owner.
I knew this because of the news articles posted at the front restaurant that tells about how the restaurant came to Madison and its owners immigrated from China to America years ago etc.
It is an interesting story.
We will be going back for full service sometime soon and I expect my rating to go up as I think this is a hidden gem in a very unassuming location.

